txt.en: '[placeholder], Gl没s Duvodiad! We beseech you to aid us once more. Your power against the Cuthraul is great, but more have been seen haunting the lands!\n\n'Will you seek out these fell spirits and banish them as well? I fear they will possess our goats and call forth Druggavar!'
'I do not know how you are able to banish these spirits, Gl没s Duvodiad, but for it, we praise you in song!'
'You are the bane of the Cuthraul, Gl没s Duvodiad.'
Dark Spirits of the Windfells -- Repeatable
The Uch-l没th were impressed by your victory against the Cuthraul at Gwyllion's Gate and seek your aid once more.
Cuthraul haunt the lands around Gavar Cadlus.\n\nIuan has asked you to banish the Cuthraul from the land.
Talk to Iuan at Gavar Cadlus
Iuan is at Gavar Cadlus in the Windfells of Enedwaith.\n\nYou should return to Iuan with tidings of your victory against the Cuthraul.
